Day 47 — Softmax Regression (Multiclass Classification)

📌 Overview

On Day 47, I learned Softmax Regression, an extension of Logistic Regression used for Multiclass Classification problems.

🧠 What I Learned

Multiclass Classification

Softmax Function

Probability Distribution across classes

Class prediction using highest probability


📈 Softmax Function

P(y=i) = \frac{e^{z_i}}{\sum_{j=1}^{k} e^{z_j}}

Converts outputs into probabilities

Sum of probabilities = 1

Used for multiple classes


💡 Key Takeaway

Softmax Regression helps classify data into more than two classes using probability distribution.
